## Rust build artifacts (1.6GB on the dev machine; regenerated from source).
target/
**/*.rs.bk

## Deno's npm cache for the Pyodide sidecar. Vendored on first run; not
## something we want in the repo. The sidecar resolves it via deno.json.
crates/host/sidecar/node_modules/

## Runtime state created by the marketplace publish endpoint. Submissions
## live here until a reviewer approves them; production deployments back this
## up out-of-band.
submissions/

## The website lives in its own repo (druidalabs/commonsc.io). Excluded so
## we don't try to embed it as a submodule.
website/
website-mockup/

## macOS / editor noise.
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/

## Local Claude session artifacts.
.claude/
